]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bEDqcOY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Another kind of dog :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/BiV8DLb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ys4ok8l.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/BiV8DLb</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LarissaMiller]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Return of the Meme (vol. 430)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9tIQswj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vaOT5J9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I am a burrito this morning for two reasons. The main reason is that it is cold: 36⁰ F in my house this AM.  The second reason is a bit of grief.... today was the day I was originally going to propose to the woman who left me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gFTnoM1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Though that means I should celebrate by myself tonight, and drink something nice from my stash. Or make the attempt.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EqiQmLj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I guess that's one way to do it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2MeOrar.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yeah, fuck that place, I hate going there.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/98ZrGE8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Mq8gJVp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love this idea.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ot0lHOl.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Being a single-celled Organism doesn't sound toooo bad.  A little dull, maybe...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Exo1YNc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Tywp55y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yeah. I miss good morning texts though.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eSCZeBK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>AAAAAAAAAAAAAA</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KL1z83o.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/q0IeMof.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GIYDj0T.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ynJJDCK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Executive dysfunction is a right bitch</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DVgHwVM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/84bMUL2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm planning to stay and become everyone's problem out of spite.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pNlMBrO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But this is still a mood when I'm alone</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FujTpuk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also I'm kind of suprosed Honorius could see it from Ravenna.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BaDQ7dh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oops.  Wrong day.  Sorry.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ib3qf2C.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zUIICul.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Rome was an amazing show.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BSTOgZi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PHauCEg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F9x9vpc.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/34zu2zC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also a mood.  Also possibly need a dominatrix like this...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ITs26b2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/987cV6A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6hpRFFo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NU3vqiF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The birding community is meme-ing the hell out of this bird.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LZok1hd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This one is probably my absolute favorite of those memes.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AAWrIxW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dZF0QLu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VVWPc0W.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/50XSI31.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TomUnEG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ztyMH80.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wxAR6Gi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Liara learned the hard way to never meet your heroes.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a3Se2nR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hTBRGYh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Not wrong...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uLXhUXG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I hope so, or I'm going to demand a refund from the management.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ekv8cEB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/E6ecLel.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mood!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8Q63Wwj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MDyqrfn.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is hysterical.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OPRX9LI.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zUeP70o.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rsG3bdZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yuuuuuuuup.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nMR7Vqf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pPqF2zh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Sqjn4iQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pippin tax!

Also today, an old poem from when I lived for a hot minute in New Mexico,  for today's poetry tax.

"Carizozo"
I am stardust 
slowly falling apart
tears and merlot staining
an antique pewter goblet
while a feathered cloak
the color of sky 
covers my bones.
 
Cycles within cycles,
universes within universes, 
dreams becoming dreams.
An ocean of time
flows through my veins
memories of landscapes
past and present 
fill my eyes.
 
I await the monsoon
