:creator><![CDATA[ixquaPandaJumper]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I feel like this</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DDcrkbM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1jIIM4s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The sad thing is that I make a concerted effort to maintain relations with others and I keep them in my thoughts and prayers all the time. Folks don’t do the same thing for me. Sometimes I feel extremely lonely and isolated. 

EDIT: Thank you to all the kind people here that reached out to me here and in DMs. 

